responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "0D69BC344B592D0B9D7852B87121D9EC", "A replica of the Megaliths we saw before. They are similar in make and appearance, but this site wasn\'t constructed by the ancient predecessors who wrested this land from the Titans. This circle here was made more recently, during the heyday of Carphin. There\'s no doubt there were rituals held here, powerful ones governed by the masters of an unknown arcana. And the similarity is no coincidence. It requires further investigation.")
